ecies of Ezekiel","slug":"event-243","score":49}],"links":[{"source":"recZOTL6wQNVaIUHR","target":"recqSg3DygQ97p2n7","label":"part of"},{"source":"recZOTL6wQNVaIUHR","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recZOTL6wQNVaIUHR","target":"reci0wRcCyZbHGbB1","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recZOTL6wQNVaIUHR","target":"recrDudv0OC99dtDt","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recZOTL6wQNVaIUHR","target":"recAS5jVEptIa8t06","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recZOTL6wQNVaIUHR","target":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recZOTL6wQNVaIUHR","target":"reclUs1vGOnRCY78z","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recZOTL6wQNVaIUHR","target":"recEP3QZ3HUmIkv4Q","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recZOTL6wQNVaIUHR","target":"recL1WV82pXaRBQ59","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recZOTL6wQNVaIUHR","target":"recIJFRcqI6KbKgXb","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recZOTL6wQNVaIUHR","target":"rec4OMrlvP8YRP40o","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recZOTL6wQNVaIUHR","target":"recZOV8ortC5HMdxI","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recZOTL6wQNVaIUHR","target":"reciqLEHEJ42oR4bN","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recZOTL6wQNVaIUHR","target":"recGUuZfUbylFAytG","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recP0WTHA3oX0MhZ7","ref":"Ezek.23.1","text":"The word of the LORD came again unto me, saying,","year":-593},{"id":"recdmU2cqA6jkfB38","ref":"Ezek.23.2","text":"Son of man, there were two women, the daughters of one mother:","year":-593},{"id":"rec5y3qqAncoOky8J","ref":"Ezek.23.3","text":"And they committed whoredoms in Egypt; they committed whoredoms in their youth: there were their breasts pressed, and there they bruised the teats of their virginity.","year":-593},{"id":"recy5KHACp6NSkayM","ref":"Ezek.23.4","text":"And the names of them were Aholah the elder, and Aholibah her sister: and they were mine, and they bare sons and daughters. Thus were their names; Samaria is Aholah, and Jerusalem Aholibah.","year":-593},{"id":"recFjFVaTdKSfxsDT","ref":"Ezek.23.5","text":"And Aholah played the harlot when she was mine; and she doted on her lovers, on the Assyrians her neighbours,","year":-593},{"id":"recwkGWsvKzlmGJGb","ref":"Ezek.23.6","text":"Which were clothed with blue, captains and rulers, all of them desirable young men, horsemen riding upon horses.","year":-593},{"id":"recez8vl1ec36w2CO","ref":"Ezek.23.7","text":"Thus she committed her whoredoms with them, with all them that were the chosen men of Assyria, and with all on whom she doted: with all their idols she defiled herself.","year":-593},{"id":"recs8cXgjwLBqdCyr","ref":"Ezek.23.8","text":"Neither left she her whoredoms brought from Egypt: for in her youth they lay with her, and they bruised the breasts of her virginity, and poured their whoredom upon her.","year":-593}]}
